==English==

===Noun===
'''congestion'''

# The act of [[gather]]ing into a [[heap]] or [[mass]]; [[accumulation]].
# An [[excess]] of [[traffic]] etc.
# Overfullness of the [[capillary]] and other [[blood vessel]]s, etc., in any locality or organ (often producing other morbid symptoms); local hyper/mia, active or passive; as, arterial congestion; venous congestion.
# An excess of [[mucus]] or [[fluid]] in the [[respiratory system]]; congestion of the [[lung]]s, or [[nasal]] congestion.

